率收敛的定义、弱大数定律、辛钦大数定律和伯努利大数定律，以及证明这些定理所需的马尔科夫不等式和切比雪夫不等式。随后介绍了中心极限定理，重点阐述了独立同分布的中心极限定理及其特例棣莫弗-拉普拉斯定理，这些定理揭示了大量独立随机变量之和的概率分布趋近于正态分布的性质。"},{"type":"element","tagName":"small","properties":{"style":"font-style: italic; opacity: 0.5"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"（由 claude-3.5-sonnet 生成摘要）"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"frontmatter":{"date":"2024-12-06"},"fields":{"slug":"/course/ptms/note/5/","category":"[{\"name\":\"课程笔记\",\"to\":\"/course/\"}]","publishedTitle":"「概率论与数理统计」V. 大数定律及中心极限定理","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#0818c8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/aee2c8b7d1731f3acc994e60fd351a49/d6737/8glRUH1O.png","srcSet":"/static/aee2c8b7d1731f3acc994e60fd351a49/39de5/8glRUH1O.png 113w,\n/static/aee2c8b7d1731f3acc994e60fd351a49/c5b22/8glRUH1O.png 227w,\n/static/aee2c8b7d1731f3acc994e60fd351a49/d6737/8glRUH1O.png 453w","sizes":"(min-width: 453px) 453px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/aee2c8b7d1731f3acc994e60fd351a49/c89c7/8glRUH1O.webp 113w,\n/static/aee2c8b7d1731f3acc994e60fd351a49/9505d/8glRUH1O.webp 227w,\n/static/aee2c8b7d1731f3acc994e60fd351a49/abd45/8glRUH1O.webp 453w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 453px) 453px, 100vw"}]},"width":453,"height":320}}}}}},{"node":{"id":"d6a749a4-211b-5027-85ad-afe7c283f16f","excerptAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"blockquote","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本篇笔记主要介绍了光学的三个重要章节：光的干涉、光的衍射和光的偏振。在光的干涉部分，详细讨论了光源的基本概念、折射率、光程等基础知识，以及杨氏双缝实验、洛埃镜实验和薄膜干涉等典型实验。在光的衍射部分，介绍了惠更斯原理，并对单缝衍射和光栅衍射进行了深入分析。最后在光的偏振部分，讨论了不同类型的光束、偏振片的原理，以及马吕斯定律和布儒斯特定律等重要规律。"},{"type":"element","tagName":"small","properties":{"style":"font-style: italic; opacity: 0.5"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"（由 claude-3.5-sonnet 生成摘要）"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"frontmatter":{"date":"2024-11-29"},"fields":{"slug":"/course/physics/note/8/","category":"[{\"name\":\"课程笔记\",\"to\":\"/course/\"}]","publishedTitle":"「大学物理(乙)」VIII. 光学","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#282858","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/cc583a099ea93874112e8d2b0e9472c9/ba08d/CQfQYJGt.png","srcSet":"/static/cc583a099ea93874112e8d2b0e9472c9/8322c/CQfQYJGt.png 168w,\n/static/cc583a099ea93874112e8d2b0e9472c9/f4791/CQfQYJGt.png 336w,\n/static/cc583a099ea93874112e8d2b0e9472c9/ba08d/CQfQYJGt.png 671w","sizes":"(min-width: 671px) 671px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/cc583a099ea93874112e8d2b0e9472c9/1b959/CQfQYJGt.webp 168w,\n/static/cc583a099ea93874112e8d2b0e9472c9/cf26f/CQfQYJGt.webp 336w,\n/static/cc583a099ea93874112e8d2b0e9472c9/e07b5/CQfQYJGt.webp 671w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 671px) 671px, 100vw"}]},"width":671,"height":448.99999999999994}}}}}},{"node":{"id":"87c03518-cfc4-5365-b91d-a764ab939834","excerptAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"blockquote","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本篇笔记介绍了随机变量的三个重要数字特征：数学期望、方差和协方差。首先讨论了离散型和连续型随机变量的数学期望定义及其性质，包括线性性和独立变量的期望。其次介绍了方差和标准差的概念、计算方法以及切比雪夫不等式，并总结了常见分布的均值与方差。最后探讨了协方差与相关系数，阐述了它们的计算公式、基本性质，以及在描述随机变量之间线性关系中的重要作用。"},{"type":"element","tagName":"small","properties":{"style":"font-style: italic; opacity: 0.5"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"（由 claude-3.5-sonnet 生成摘要）"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"frontmatter":{"date":"2024-11-26"},"fields":{"slug":"/course/ptms/note/4/","category":"[{\"name\":\"课程笔记\",\"to\":\"/course/\"}]","publishedTitle":"「概率论与数理统计」IV. 随机变量的数字特征","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#0818c8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/aee2c8b7d